title: Franchise value of the New York Mets 2002 to 2019
yAxis: Franchise value in million U.S. dollars
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Franchise value in million U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 18.
In general Franchise value in million U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
The highest Franchise value in million U.S. dollars, of value 2300.0 was reached at Year 2019
Minimum Franchise value in million U.S. dollars about 442.0 was reached at Year 2004
